29
00:02:48,649 --> 00:02:50,090
This is my marriage.

30
00:02:50,489 --> 00:02:52,090
Of course, I'll decide on it myself.

31
00:02:53,289 --> 00:02:54,689
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

32
00:02:55,569 --> 00:02:57,170
