56
00:04:05,530 --> 00:04:06,489
Take your time.

57
00:04:06,569 --> 00:04:07,450
You'll figure it out.

58
00:04:10,849 --> 00:04:11,450
Yeah.

59
00:04:12,530 --> 00:04:15,250
The last time has to be a bit special.

60
00:04:23,490 --> 00:04:24,010
Shan Hu.

61
00:04:24,450 --> 00:04:25,409
Run an errand for me.

62
00:04:25,650 --> 00:04:26,969
Take this list to His Majesty

63
00:04:27,369 --> 00:04:28,650
