64
00:04:30,450 --> 00:04:32,170
Ten deep-sea fish gallbladders.

65
00:04:32,330 --> 00:04:33,490
Ten Beiming serpent scales.

66
00:04:33,849 --> 00:04:35,369
Ten Zhaoyuan red pearls.

67
00:04:35,650 --> 00:04:37,170
A melon-sized

68
00:04:37,490 --> 00:04:38,650
ten-thousand-year ice crystal.

69
00:04:39,010 --> 00:04:39,809
Princess.

70
00:04:40,089 --> 00:04:41,330
Are you emptying the treasury

71
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:42,210
