73
00:04:44,289 --> 00:04:44,890
By the way,

74
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:46,249
I also need two experts

75
00:04:46,289 --> 00:04:47,409
to watch the furnace,

76
00:04:47,770 --> 00:04:49,450
preferably of ice and fire attributes,

77
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,330
respectively.

78
00:04:50,450 --> 00:04:51,170
Yes, Princess.

79
00:04:51,249 --> 00:04:52,170
