83
00:05:10,689 --> 00:05:11,450
Bring her back

84
00:05:11,450 --> 00:05:12,730
to prepare for the wedding.

85
00:05:13,689 --> 00:05:14,288
Understood.

86
00:05:14,770 --> 00:05:15,730
But this is

87
00:05:16,409 --> 00:05:17,210
not urgent.

88
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:18,849
You don't need to rush.

89
00:05:19,369 --> 00:05:20,129
Health comes first.

90
00:05:23,210 --> 00:05:23,730
Master.

91
00:05:24,450 --> 00:05:25,289
Even if it's urgent,

92
00:05:25,809 --> 00:05:26,569
I can't rush.

93
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:27,569
I've been

94
00:05:27,569 --> 00:05:28,490
feeling unwell.

95
00:05:29,129 --> 00:05:30,010
I'm always dizzy

96
00:05:30,210 --> 00:05:31,369
and can't even ride a mount.

97
00:05:31,689 --> 00:05:32,610
Wherever I go,

98
00:05:32,890 --> 00:05:34,210
I walk slowly.

99
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,490
What a convenient time.

100
00:05:37,730 --> 00:05:38,689
Besides,

101
00:05:39,129 --> 00:05:39,809
I finally arrived

102
00:05:39,969 --> 00:05:41,170
in Cang Xuan's turf.

103
00:05:41,409 --> 00:05:43,210
I deserve some rest, anyway.

104
00:05:43,409 --> 00:05:45,089
And I have to visit a few friends

105
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:46,650
in Zhiyi City.

106
00:05:47,289 --> 00:05:47,849
Master.

107
00:05:48,289 --> 00:05:49,650
You won't see me

108
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:51,170
in a long time.

109
00:05:53,010 --> 00:05:53,650
