112
00:06:32,610 --> 00:06:33,330
Chishui Xian.

113
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:34,249
More spirit power.

114
00:06:36,490 --> 00:06:37,289
Yu Jiang, stop.

115
00:06:56,170 --> 00:06:56,784
That's enough.

116
00:07:05,730 --> 00:07:06,369
Made it.

117
00:07:08,170 --> 00:07:09,770
What on earth are you making

118
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:11,930
that you need two experts?

119
00:07:12,969 --> 00:07:13,930
It's just a pill.

120
00:07:16,369 --> 00:07:18,050
I thought Nian was extravagant enough.

121
00:07:18,210 --> 00:07:19,529
I didn't expect that

122
00:07:19,689 --> 00:07:22,289
she's nothing comparable to you.

123
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:25,369
I'm going to Zhiyi in a while.

124
00:07:26,969 --> 00:07:27,849
Do as you wish.

125
00:07:28,369 --> 00:07:30,770
I have been weary and exhausted

126
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:32,249
from the journey.

127
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:34,409
I need a few days of rest.

128
00:07:34,890 --> 00:07:35,770
No rush.

129
00:07:40,210 --> 00:07:41,210
To the usual place.

130
00:07:41,369 --> 00:07:41,936
Be fast.

131
00:07:42,249 --> 00:07:43,289
Please rest assured.

132
00:07:48,689 --> 00:07:49,249
Thank you.

133
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:07,770
To Qingshui Town again?

134
00:08:07,890 --> 00:08:08,450
Yes.

135
00:08:10,969 --> 00:08:12,569
Anything wrong on Chenrong Mountain?

136
00:08:13,330 --> 00:08:14,010
Why is she suddenly

137
00:08:14,050 --> 00:08:15,409
sending something to Qingshui Town

138
00:08:15,689 --> 00:08:17,129
when it hasn't been three months?

139
00:08:17,289 --> 00:08:18,490
Everything is fine there.

140
00:08:18,930 --> 00:08:19,770
But the Chishui Family

141
00:08:19,969 --> 00:08:21,210
has been acting weird.

142
00:08:21,809 --> 00:08:22,330
Chief.

143
00:08:23,010 --> 00:08:24,450
Should we intercept this box

144
00:08:24,569 --> 00:08:25,969
or take a look inside?

145
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:28,689
Send it fast.

146
00:08:28,849 --> 00:08:29,450
Do not delay.

147
00:08:29,569 --> 00:08:30,096
Understood.

148
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:33,650
Prepare the mounts.

149
00:08:34,090 --> 00:08:34,770
Find out what

150
00:08:34,770 --> 00:08:35,970
Fenglong has been doing.

151
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:36,850
Understood.

152
00:08:37,290 --> 00:08:38,090
Prepare some...

153
00:08:40,129 --> 00:08:40,809
Chief.

154
00:08:40,809 --> 00:08:42,410
You should rest first.

155
00:08:46,809 --> 00:08:47,530
Go to Chishui.

156
00:08:48,010 --> 00:08:48,592
Understood.

157
00:09:24,049 --> 00:09:25,249
They make nice braised dishes.

158
00:09:26,169 --> 00:09:27,129
Try and see

159
00:09:27,609 --> 00:09:28,330
if you like them.

160
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:31,770
My tastes have changed.

161
00:09:33,129 --> 00:09:34,450
I no longer like these.

162
00:09:37,929 --> 00:09:39,369
Then try the green plum wine.

163
00:09:40,650 --> 00:09:42,010
Chief Tushan, didn't you hear

164
00:09:42,010 --> 00:09:43,169
what I just said?

165
00:09:43,609 --> 00:09:45,609
I said my taste had changed.

166
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:49,090
The wine I love to drink now

167
00:09:50,249 --> 00:09:51,770
is the Lianhua Liquor from Chishui.

168
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:05,169
It just happens

169
00:10:05,970 --> 00:10:06,809
that I have

170
00:10:06,809 --> 00:10:07,970
something to tell you.

171
00:10:10,609 --> 00:10:11,929
Fenglong and I are getting married.

172
00:10:13,290 --> 00:10:15,010
You're a good friend of Fenglong.

173
00:10:15,330 --> 00:10:17,129
Please come early for the wedding

174
00:10:17,410 --> 00:10:18,129
for fine wine.

175
00:10:21,970 --> 00:10:22,489
Alright.

176
00:10:23,049 --> 00:10:24,530
I've said everything I needed to.

177
00:10:25,129 --> 00:10:27,210
I won't disturb you anymore.

178
00:10:31,569 --> 00:10:32,129
Miao Pu.

179
00:10:32,290 --> 00:10:32,890
Shan Hu.

180
00:10:41,970 --> 00:10:42,530
Chief.

181
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:49,929
Princess.

182
00:10:53,330 --> 00:10:53,970
Princess.

183
00:10:57,090 --> 00:10:57,809
Princess.

184
00:11:01,770 --> 00:11:02,410
Princess.

185
00:11:03,450 --> 00:11:04,049
What's wrong?

186
00:11:05,010 --> 00:11:05,689
Princess.

187
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:06,850
Are you alright?

188
00:11:08,489 --> 00:11:09,489
Why would you ask that?

189
00:11:13,129 --> 00:11:14,169
Do all the major clans

190
00:11:14,330 --> 00:11:15,809
know about my wedding?

191
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:18,010
Princess of Haoling is marrying

192
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:19,129
Chief Chishui.

193
00:11:19,369 --> 00:11:20,609
The major clans must have

194
00:11:20,609 --> 00:11:21,890
heard about it.

195
00:11:24,010 --> 00:11:25,770
Chief Tushan didn't seem to know.

196
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:26,809
That's right.

197
00:11:27,249 --> 00:11:29,169
He seems to have just found out.

198
00:11:30,689 --> 00:11:32,450
The wedding will take place soon.

199
00:11:33,049 --> 00:11:34,770
But His Majesty and the King of Haoling

200
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,249
kept the news tightly sealed.

201
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:39,049
The Chishui clan would not
announce it rashly.

202
00:11:39,689 --> 00:11:41,410
So Chief Tushan may not have

203
00:11:41,450 --> 00:11:42,410
heard about it.

204
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:44,249
Their Majesties are not

205
00:11:44,249 --> 00:11:45,369
very enthusiastic

206
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:46,929
and they still haven't announced it.

207
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:47,970
It seems as if

208
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:49,929
they're waiting for you
to change your mind.

209
00:11:50,210 --> 00:11:50,770
Nonsense.

210
00:12:04,650 --> 00:12:05,290
I made

211
00:12:06,249 --> 00:12:08,770
these dishes for you.

212
00:12:09,689 --> 00:12:11,530
What made you so happy

213
00:12:12,369 --> 00:12:14,049
that you cooked in person?

214
00:12:16,010 --> 00:12:17,330
I'm heading back tomorrow

215
00:12:17,809 --> 00:12:18,890
to wait for the wedding.

216
00:12:19,249 --> 00:12:20,650
I'm here to bid you farewell.

217
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:24,530
So soon?

218
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:26,929
I want to

219
00:12:27,090 --> 00:12:28,090
spend some time with Father.

220
00:12:34,689 --> 00:12:36,249
Actually, there's no need to rush.

221
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:39,450
We can simply postpone the wedding.

222
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:43,929
That's not how things work.

223
00:12:47,530 --> 00:12:48,290
Xuan.

224
00:12:56,129 --> 00:12:57,410
I can't bear to leave you.

225
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:03,010
It's not like I'm never coming back.

226
00:13:04,010 --> 00:13:05,249
Maybe I'll come right back

227
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:07,049
after the wedding.

228
00:13:07,850 --> 00:13:08,729
Just think of it

229
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:09,689
as a usual parting.

230
00:13:10,450 --> 00:13:11,689
I'm just going back

231
00:13:11,689 --> 00:13:13,010
to visit Father.

232
00:13:13,650 --> 00:13:14,450
We are only parting

233
00:13:14,450 --> 00:13:15,369
for a short while.

234
00:13:20,450 --> 00:13:22,169
It's different this time.

235
00:13:22,450 --> 00:13:23,290
How?

236
00:13:28,609 --> 00:13:29,970
No matter where you went,

237
00:13:30,770 --> 00:13:32,129
I could always bring you back.

238
00:13:33,530 --> 00:13:34,249
But

239
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:38,249
it's different now.

240
00:13:39,890 --> 00:13:41,489
No matter how long and how far

241
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:44,049
we were apart,

242
00:13:46,010 --> 00:13:47,650
we had no one but each other.

243
00:13:49,369 --> 00:13:50,609
Be it on Zhaoyun Peak,

244
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:53,569
Wushen Mountain,

245
00:13:53,569 --> 00:13:54,489
or Chenrong Mountain,

246
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:58,929
the two of us shared

247
00:13:59,689 --> 00:14:00,530
weal and woe.

248
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:03,929
Be it in poverty,

249
00:14:04,689 --> 00:14:05,770
wealth,

250
00:14:06,210 --> 00:14:07,569
or grave danger with our lives

251
00:14:08,770 --> 00:14:09,489
at risk,

252
00:14:12,489 --> 00:14:14,249
we were each other's support

253
00:14:15,489 --> 00:14:16,410
and family.

254
00:14:19,049 --> 00:14:20,010
But from now on,

255
00:14:20,929 --> 00:14:22,330
you will have your family

256
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:25,049
and children.

257
00:14:27,569 --> 00:14:28,850
I'm no longer your only one.

258
00:14:31,569 --> 00:14:32,929
Am I being selfish?

259
00:14:39,049 --> 00:14:40,609
We have grown up. That's all.

260
00:14:41,369 --> 00:14:42,689
We have grown up.

261
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:46,970
Let's drink by bowls

262
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:48,609
and get wasted.

263
00:14:49,809 --> 00:14:50,320
Alright.

264
00:15:00,650 --> 00:15:01,650
Cheers, Xuan.

265
00:15:12,770 --> 00:15:13,369
Xiaoyao.

266
00:15:15,970 --> 00:15:17,850
Do you remember how I sent you away

267
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:20,450
to Mount Jade

268
00:15:21,689 --> 00:15:23,330
from Zhaoyun Peak when we were kids?

269
00:15:27,210 --> 00:15:28,729
I thought I couldn't keep you

270
00:15:30,369 --> 00:15:31,650
because I wasn't the king.

271
00:15:33,929 --> 00:15:35,090
I thought once I became

272
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:36,569
the King of Xiyan,

273
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:37,929
then I could

274
00:15:38,609 --> 00:15:40,169
keep you forever.

275
00:15:41,169 --> 00:15:43,569
But now I am the King of Xiyan.

276
00:15:46,169 --> 00:15:47,809
I still have to send you away.

277
00:16:39,129 --> 00:16:41,210
It's all my fault.

278
00:16:43,890 --> 00:16:46,850
I let them get close to you.

279
00:16:48,369 --> 00:16:51,090
I let them into your heart.

280
00:16:55,609 --> 00:16:56,929
It's not your fault.

281
00:16:57,770 --> 00:16:59,169
Whatever you do

282
00:16:59,290 --> 00:17:00,249
is right.

283
00:17:00,970 --> 00:17:02,249
You did nothing wrong.

284
00:17:02,450 --> 00:17:02,970
No.

285
00:17:06,369 --> 00:17:07,129
I was wrong.

286
00:17:08,290 --> 00:17:12,010
I was terribly wrong.

287
00:17:15,410 --> 00:17:16,129
Xiaoyao.

288
00:17:19,209 --> 00:17:19,824
Today,

289
00:17:20,729 --> 00:17:23,089
I shall speak my mind.

290
00:17:23,570 --> 00:17:24,969
I must confess.

291
00:17:25,249 --> 00:17:26,170
Go ahead.

292
00:17:28,650 --> 00:17:29,570
I like you.

293
00:17:32,089 --> 00:17:34,290
I only like you.

294
00:17:37,650 --> 00:17:38,930
Don't marry Fenglong.

295
00:17:39,410 --> 00:17:40,129
Marry me.

