351
00:19:48,624 --> 00:19:49,129
Father...

352
00:19:55,570 --> 00:19:56,249
Your marriage

353
00:19:56,449 --> 00:19:58,010
will decide how you live

354
00:19:58,050 --> 00:19:59,089
from now on.

355
00:19:59,609 --> 00:20:00,449
If you have

356
00:20:00,449 --> 00:20:01,369
no regrets

357
00:20:01,530 --> 00:20:02,249
or hesitation,

358
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:03,690
then why can't you

359
