♪Scenes unfurl within myself♪

394
00:23:25,648 --> 00:23:29,360
♪It's the way back. It's the way home♪

395
00:23:29,808 --> 00:23:32,976
♪Life is like dancing in the snow♪

396
00:23:33,392 --> 00:23:36,592
♪It's the end♪

397
00:23:42,452 --> 00:23:45,392
(West River Bank, Qingshui Town)

398
00:23:46,170 --> 00:23:47,410
My older brother tortured me

399
00:23:47,410 --> 00:23:48,650
in a dungeon for three years.

400
00:23:49,570 --> 00:23:50,729
I lost all my spirit power

401
00:23:50,969 --> 00:23:52,129
and my limbs were ruined.

402
00:23:53,770 --> 00:23:55,849
Even my throat
was scorched by the spirit fire.

403
00:23:56,849 --> 00:23:58,209
I couldn't say a single word.

404
00:23:58,729 --> 00:24:00,249
He thought I was destroyed

405
00:24:01,489 --> 00:24:02,930
and threw me into the river.

406
00:24:05,170 --> 00:24:07,129
I had long lost the will to live.

407
00:24:08,290 --> 00:24:09,410
Semi-unconscious,

408
00:24:10,369 --> 00:24:11,650
I didn't know how long I drifted

409
00:24:11,810 --> 00:24:12,849
until I ended here.

410
00:24:19,129 --> 00:24:20,129
You were sealed

411
00:24:20,930 --> 00:24:22,290
and didn't see me.

412
00:24:23,410 --> 00:24:24,530
My flesh was rotting

413
00:24:25,369 --> 00:24:26,329
with a stench.

414
00:24:27,449 --> 00:24:28,849
I barely looked like a human.

415
00:24:30,729 --> 00:24:31,570
Those who saw me

416
00:24:31,570 --> 00:24:33,010
covered their noses and avoided me.

417
00:24:34,849 --> 00:24:35,969
Even those who knew me

418
00:24:35,969 --> 00:24:37,290
wouldn't come closer.

419
00:24:39,410 --> 00:24:40,329
Only Xiaoliu.

420
00:24:41,129 --> 00:24:42,729
Only Xiaoliu held me

421
00:24:42,729 --> 00:24:43,930
without any disdain.

422
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:47,690
She didn't mind the stench

423
00:24:48,489 --> 00:24:50,369
or the terrible wounds on my body.

424
00:24:50,810 --> 00:24:51,810
She treated my wounds,

425
00:24:53,410 --> 00:24:54,410
washed my hair,

426
00:24:55,249 --> 00:24:56,369
and fed me.

427
00:24:58,249 --> 00:25:00,209
She told me stories
so that I wasn't bored.

428
00:25:01,410 --> 00:25:02,930
What a nice girl.

429
00:25:04,369 --> 00:25:05,690
But I lost her.

430
00:25:11,570 --> 00:25:13,089
What would Ye Shiqi do

431
00:25:16,969 --> 00:25:18,489
at this point?

432
00:25:26,890 --> 00:25:27,570
This imperial edict

433
00:25:27,570 --> 00:25:29,329
has been sent
throughout Xiyan and Haoling?

434
00:25:31,570 --> 00:25:32,089
Your Majesty.

435
00:25:32,650 --> 00:25:33,650
We followed the order

436
00:25:34,010 --> 00:25:35,170
given by the Great Emperor.

437
00:25:42,570 --> 00:25:43,170
Grandfather.

438
00:25:59,849 --> 00:26:00,849
I don't get it.

439
00:26:01,729 --> 00:26:02,770
Why would you help Fenglong,

440
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:03,930
the outsider?

441
00:26:06,930 --> 00:26:08,369
I'm not helping Fenglong.

442
00:26:09,690 --> 00:26:11,969
I'm helping Xiaoyao.

443
00:26:12,770 --> 00:26:16,690
Xiaoyao is the only child
Heng left behind.

444
00:26:17,170 --> 00:26:19,570
She wishes to live
a peaceful and stable life.

445
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:20,810
Shouldn't I grant her that?

446
00:26:20,810 --> 00:26:22,770
Xiaoyao does not like Fenglong.

447
00:26:23,170 --> 00:26:24,089
She doesn't know

448
00:26:24,089 --> 00:26:25,290
what she wants.

449
00:26:25,410 --> 00:26:26,249
Then what

450
00:26:26,969 --> 00:26:28,489
do you think she wants?

451
00:26:29,209 --> 00:26:30,209
To always follow you?

452
00:26:30,890 --> 00:26:35,329
To always be embroiled
in court and infighting?

453
00:26:36,010 --> 00:26:37,810
To always be cautious

454
00:26:38,089 --> 00:26:39,449
and make sacrifices?

455
00:26:43,449 --> 00:26:45,449
Both of you grew up

456
00:26:45,690 --> 00:26:47,170
on Zhaoyun Peak.

457
00:26:47,570 --> 00:26:50,170
But ever since Xiaoyao was cast adrift
among the common folk,

458
00:26:50,690 --> 00:26:52,369
she's been different from you.

459
00:26:52,930 --> 00:26:53,810
She wants

460
00:26:54,449 --> 00:26:57,890
a leisurely life of a commoner,
which is peaceful and stable.

461
00:26:58,570 --> 00:27:00,810
It's not like I can't give her
what she wants.

462
00:27:01,129 --> 00:27:02,209
I just need...

463
00:27:02,290 --> 00:27:03,449
Some time.

464
00:27:04,290 --> 00:27:04,969
Right?

465
00:27:07,290 --> 00:27:07,969
Cang Xuan.

466
00:27:09,050 --> 00:27:10,369
I've been in your position

467
00:27:10,369 --> 00:27:11,249
before.

468
00:27:11,530 --> 00:27:14,089
I know more than anyone

469
00:27:14,690 --> 00:27:17,050
that as long as one sits on that throne,

470
00:27:17,050 --> 00:27:18,369
he always needs to

471
00:27:18,609 --> 00:27:20,290
be cautious and vigilant

472
00:27:21,329 --> 00:27:23,089
and make sacrifices.

473
00:27:24,930 --> 00:27:26,369
You need some time.

474
00:27:26,609 --> 00:27:27,690
But even you

475
00:27:28,290 --> 00:27:30,290
don't know how long it will be.

476
00:27:39,690 --> 00:27:41,770
What did you promise your aunt?

477
00:27:47,969 --> 00:27:49,089
I promised to

478
00:27:53,170 --> 00:27:54,410
protect Xiaoyao.

479
00:27:55,489 --> 00:27:57,969
Let Xiaoyao get married

480
00:27:58,290 --> 00:27:59,849
and do what she wants to do.

481
00:27:59,849 --> 00:28:01,530
Give her the life she wants.

482
00:28:02,650 --> 00:28:04,489
This is how you protect her.

483
00:28:30,609 --> 00:28:31,849
Poinciana flower wreath.

484
00:28:32,209 --> 00:28:33,089
I made it for you.

485
00:28:49,969 --> 00:28:50,650
Xiaoyao.

486
00:28:51,449 --> 00:28:52,410
What are you waiting for?

487
00:28:53,530 --> 00:28:54,249
I don't know.

488
00:28:55,249 --> 00:28:56,530
But you're waiting.

489
00:28:57,449 --> 00:28:59,089
Maybe I'm waiting for destiny.

490
00:29:00,729 --> 00:29:01,410
Destiny?

491
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:03,089
What is destiny?

492
00:29:05,810 --> 00:29:06,449
I don't know.

493
00:29:07,650 --> 00:29:08,449
Xiaoyao.

494
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:10,609
You're not being serious.

495
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:12,449
You keep saying you don't know.

496
00:29:16,329 --> 00:29:17,650
I really don't know.

497
00:29:18,890 --> 00:29:19,849
Isn't it true that

498
00:29:20,050 --> 00:29:22,089
none of us know anything about life?

499
00:29:23,489 --> 00:29:24,770
We don't know when

500
00:29:25,609 --> 00:29:26,890
we'll be born or die.

501
00:29:27,930 --> 00:29:28,810
We don't know if

502
00:29:28,810 --> 00:29:30,449
lovers can get married.

503
00:29:31,170 --> 00:29:32,650
We don't know if loving couples

504
00:29:33,129 --> 00:29:34,410
can stay together forever.

505
00:29:35,530 --> 00:29:36,810
We don't even know

506
00:29:37,010 --> 00:29:38,650
what will happen tomorrow.

507
00:29:40,729 --> 00:29:42,609
We don't know.

508
00:29:46,489 --> 00:29:47,530
Back then,

509
00:29:47,729 --> 00:29:49,530
I thought I was the Princess of Haoling

510
00:29:49,810 --> 00:29:52,209
and could have anything I desired.

511
00:29:53,209 --> 00:29:54,249
But I didn't know that

512
00:29:54,249 --> 00:29:55,650
Xuan would suddenly leave Haoling

513
00:29:56,410 --> 00:29:58,770
and become the King of Xiyan.

514
00:30:00,050 --> 00:30:01,449
Nor did I know that

515
00:30:03,010 --> 00:30:04,849
he would marry someone else.

516
00:30:07,530 --> 00:30:09,129
And now, I don't know

517
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:10,930
if I can

518
00:30:11,609 --> 00:30:13,290
be with him or not.

519
00:30:25,609 --> 00:30:26,209
Xiaoyao.

520
00:30:27,890 --> 00:30:29,530
What are you expecting?

521
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:32,650
Father asked me to wait for a week.

522
00:30:33,849 --> 00:30:35,089
It is destiny

523
00:30:35,849 --> 00:30:37,810
if nothing happens within the week.

524
00:30:38,810 --> 00:30:41,690
It is also destiny if something happens.

525
00:30:43,129 --> 00:30:45,170
When you can't change anything

526
00:30:46,050 --> 00:30:47,129
and don't know how to

527
00:30:47,129 --> 00:30:48,050
make a change,

528
00:30:50,729 --> 00:30:52,410
it seems all you can do is wait.

529
00:31:16,209 --> 00:31:17,050
It's your turn.

530
00:31:29,329 --> 00:31:30,010
I've lost.

531
00:31:31,010 --> 00:31:33,290
Your mind is unsettled.
Of course you will lose.

532
00:31:35,609 --> 00:31:36,729
I'll go out for a walk.

533
00:31:36,849 --> 00:31:37,729
I'll come with you.

534
00:31:42,570 --> 00:31:43,650
What are you worried about?

535
00:31:46,249 --> 00:31:47,329
You think I'll stop Xiaoyao

536
00:31:47,329 --> 00:31:48,369
from getting married?

537
00:31:55,329 --> 00:31:56,489
I am the King of Xiyan.

538
00:31:57,849 --> 00:31:58,969
With the power I have,

539
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:02,010
I can directly issue an imperial decree

540
00:32:02,010 --> 00:32:03,410
to cancel the wedding.

541
00:32:05,010 --> 00:32:06,129
Or I can give

542
00:32:07,249 --> 00:32:09,010
a secret command to the assassins.

543
00:32:09,010 --> 00:32:10,570
They will fulfill my wishes

544
00:32:10,570 --> 00:32:12,290
at all costs.

545
00:32:15,209 --> 00:32:16,290
Just a single word

546
00:32:19,050 --> 00:32:21,089
and I could avoid the pain.

547
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:25,570
But I will not do so.

548
00:32:27,729 --> 00:32:29,449
Because this is what Xiaoyao wants.

549
00:32:31,329 --> 00:32:32,449
No matter what she wants,

550
00:32:32,449 --> 00:32:33,530
I will give it to her.

551
00:32:36,930 --> 00:32:38,770
I will take out my heart for her

552
00:32:41,209 --> 00:32:42,050
if she wants it.

553
00:32:43,410 --> 00:32:45,449
This is the life of a king.

554
00:32:46,930 --> 00:32:48,489
We gain everything.

555
00:32:48,729 --> 00:32:50,290
But we also lose everything.

556
00:32:50,810 --> 00:32:52,209
Grandfather, I am not like you.

557
00:32:55,570 --> 00:32:57,729
I have never yearned to be a king.

558
00:33:00,690 --> 00:33:01,890
I lost my father,

559
00:33:03,050 --> 00:33:04,249
my mother,

560
00:33:05,089 --> 00:33:06,209
my grandmother,

561
00:33:06,209 --> 00:33:07,410
and my aunt.

562
00:33:08,729 --> 00:33:10,690
I have come this far.

563
00:33:12,890 --> 00:33:13,890
What I want

564
00:33:13,890 --> 00:33:15,089
is to protect

565
00:33:15,089 --> 00:33:16,729
whatever I have left.

566
00:33:21,290 --> 00:33:22,449
But when I have

567
00:33:22,449 --> 00:33:24,129
the power to protect everything,

568
00:33:27,570 --> 00:33:28,369
I have lost

569
00:33:28,369 --> 00:33:29,810
the only person I want to protect.

570
00:34:59,330 --> 00:35:00,810
(We won't ever be parted)

571
00:35:01,090 --> 00:35:02,850
as long as I'm your little sister.

572
00:35:03,889 --> 00:35:04,489
Alright.

573
00:35:04,689 --> 00:35:05,689
You're always my sister.

574
00:35:05,689 --> 00:35:07,290
And I'm your big brother forever.

575
00:35:07,449 --> 00:35:08,370
No matter what happens,

576
00:35:08,449 --> 00:35:09,729
we'll be together forever.

577
00:35:10,090 --> 00:35:11,050
Deal.

578
00:35:11,050 --> 00:35:12,090
Together forever.

579
00:35:12,090 --> 00:35:14,010
We will never be parted.

580
00:35:14,050 --> 00:35:14,850
It's a promise.

581
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:52,976
♪You appear at the end of the river♪

582
00:35:53,712 --> 00:35:57,360
♪But disappear as clouds rise♪

583
00:35:58,064 --> 00:36:01,744
♪You appear when I look up♪

584
00:36:02,416 --> 00:36:06,192
♪But disappear as I lower my head♪

