00:36:06,736 --> 00:36:10,544
♪You appear in the snow♪

586
00:36:11,152 --> 00:36:14,832
♪But disappear as flowers bloom♪

587
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:18,160
♪You appear as the smoke rises♪

588
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:22,800
♪You disappear in the light♪

589
00:36:30,689 --> 00:36:31,290
Princess.

590
00:36:31,409 --> 00:36:32,649
Do you want this rouge?

591
00:36:32,649 --> 00:36:33,729
Or that one?

592
00:36:34,649 --> 00:36:35,249
Either is fine.

593
00:36:36,969 --> 00:36:37,530
Princess.

594
00:36:38,249 --> 00:36:39,370
King of Haoling

595
00:36:39,489 --> 00:36:40,810
gave you a phoenix pendant.

596
00:36:41,010 --> 00:36:41,969
Great Emperor

597
00:36:42,090 --> 00:36:43,850
gave you a cloud-pattern pendant.

598
00:36:44,010 --> 00:36:45,570
Which one would you wear today?

599
00:36:45,729 --> 00:36:46,370
Either works.

600
00:36:49,610 --> 00:36:51,449
I've never seen a bride like you.

601
00:36:53,850 --> 00:36:55,810
What should a bride be like?

602
00:36:56,729 --> 00:36:58,050
If one day

603
00:36:58,050 --> 00:36:59,169
I can marry Cang Xuan,

604
00:36:59,330 --> 00:37:00,770
I will definitely be nervous.

605
00:37:01,209 --> 00:37:02,409
I'll also be a bit scared

606
00:37:02,489 --> 00:37:03,850
that I'm not pretty enough.

607
00:37:04,649 --> 00:37:06,530
From my accessories and jewelry

608
00:37:06,649 --> 00:37:07,729
to the color of my rouge,

609
00:37:07,770 --> 00:37:08,850
I will hand-pick everything.

610
00:37:09,249 --> 00:37:10,249
I will look forward

611
00:37:10,370 --> 00:37:11,810
to my future with him.

612
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:14,169
It will make me smile.

613
00:37:16,130 --> 00:37:17,249
And I'll be reluctant

614
00:37:17,610 --> 00:37:19,090
to leave my father and mother.

615
00:37:19,209 --> 00:37:20,689
I will surely cry.

616
00:37:21,370 --> 00:37:22,209
Are you anticipating

617
00:37:22,209 --> 00:37:23,169
or are you afraid?

618
00:37:23,169 --> 00:37:23,969
Will you cry

619
00:37:23,969 --> 00:37:24,770
or will you laugh?

620
00:37:25,889 --> 00:37:28,489
This is what every woman is like
when she marries

621
00:37:28,489 --> 00:37:29,249
the man she loves.

622
00:37:29,610 --> 00:37:31,090
Crying and laughing.

623
00:37:31,290 --> 00:37:33,010
Anticipating and afraid.

624
00:37:39,449 --> 00:37:39,969
Xiaoyao.

625
00:37:41,010 --> 00:37:42,689
Do you like Chief Chishui?

626
00:38:10,010 --> 00:38:10,649
Boatman.

627
00:38:12,249 --> 00:38:13,130
Boatman.

628
00:38:16,489 --> 00:38:17,330
Boatman.

629
00:38:24,050 --> 00:38:24,850
(I am content)

630
00:38:24,850 --> 00:38:25,729
(with my lot.)

631
00:38:26,050 --> 00:38:27,249
Wherever I go is home.

632
00:38:55,570 --> 00:38:57,489
I taught you how to protect yourself.

633
00:39:00,850 --> 00:39:02,489
Yet you just muddle along

634
00:39:03,929 --> 00:39:05,409
and idle around.

635
00:39:08,850 --> 00:39:10,489
Did you ask for my permission?

636
00:39:13,489 --> 00:39:14,090
Xiaoyao.

637
00:39:14,409 --> 00:39:15,050
Did you hear me?

638
00:39:15,570 --> 00:39:16,969
Do you like Chief Chishui or not?

639
00:39:19,489 --> 00:39:20,489
Fenglong is a handsome man

640
00:39:21,249 --> 00:39:22,010
from a good family.

641
00:39:22,530 --> 00:39:24,050
He has a good temperament.

642
00:39:24,649 --> 00:39:26,610
Which noble lady in Dahuang

643
00:39:26,649 --> 00:39:28,130
wouldn't like such a gentleman?

644
00:39:28,489 --> 00:39:29,729
I don't care if the others

645
00:39:29,729 --> 00:39:30,929
like Chishui Fenglong

646
00:39:30,929 --> 00:39:31,649
or not.

647
00:39:32,209 --> 00:39:33,850
I'm asking if you like him.

648
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:40,810
Great Princess.

649
00:39:40,810 --> 00:39:41,489
We have arrived.

650
00:39:41,770 --> 00:39:42,770
You can get off now.

651
00:39:45,130 --> 00:39:45,810
I see.

652
00:39:47,810 --> 00:39:49,209
You haven't changed
into the wedding dress.

653
00:39:49,929 --> 00:39:50,810
And the jewelry.

654
00:39:51,530 --> 00:39:52,770
Hurry. Don't be late.

655
00:39:52,770 --> 00:39:53,449
Hurry.

656
00:39:58,330 --> 00:39:58,969
Stand up, please.

657
00:39:59,649 --> 00:40:00,449
Hands up, please.

658
00:40:14,889 --> 00:40:15,504
Chief.

659
00:40:15,850 --> 00:40:17,130
Princess' boat has arrived.

660
00:40:22,249 --> 00:40:23,010
Look at me.

661
00:40:23,249 --> 00:40:24,530
Is there anything improper?

662
00:40:25,810 --> 00:40:26,570
Not at all.

663
00:40:26,770 --> 00:40:27,929
Don't be so anxious.

664
00:40:30,449 --> 00:40:31,489
I have to be anxious.

665
00:40:32,010 --> 00:40:32,889
I'm marrying

666
00:40:33,050 --> 00:40:33,850
the most

667
00:40:33,850 --> 00:40:34,929
distinguished lady in Dahuang.

668
00:40:35,249 --> 00:40:36,290
Sister of the King of Xiyan.

669
00:40:36,530 --> 00:40:37,489
Daughter of King of Haoling.

670
00:40:37,729 --> 00:40:38,810
Disciple of the Queen Mother.

671
00:40:38,810 --> 00:40:40,050
Then you should be more at ease.

672
00:40:40,290 --> 00:40:41,449
Because throughout Dahuang,

673
00:40:41,610 --> 00:40:42,850
only you deserve the princess

674
00:40:43,290 --> 00:40:44,050
with your status

675
00:40:44,169 --> 00:40:45,010
and ability.

676
00:40:45,249 --> 00:40:46,090
Makes sense.

677
00:40:46,449 --> 00:40:47,120
You'll be rewarded.

678
00:40:49,249 --> 00:40:52,169
- The princess has arrived.
- The princess has arrived.

679
00:40:52,649 --> 00:40:53,689
Let's greet the bride.

680
00:42:03,770 --> 00:42:05,370
She's not only the most prestigious

681
00:42:06,050 --> 00:42:07,889
but also the prettiest lady in Dahuang.

682
00:42:33,729 --> 00:42:34,290
(You)

683
00:42:35,810 --> 00:42:36,729
(saved me.)

684
00:42:38,330 --> 00:42:40,090
(I am)

685
00:42:40,889 --> 00:42:42,649
(your servant.)

686
00:42:44,130 --> 00:42:45,090
(Please name me.)

687
00:42:46,689 --> 00:42:47,330
Beggar.

688
00:42:48,249 --> 00:42:49,489
Starting today,

689
00:42:49,770 --> 00:42:50,810
you'll be Ye Shiqi.

690
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

691
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

692
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

693
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

694
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

695
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

696
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

697
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

698
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

699
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

700
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

701
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

702
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

703
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

704
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

705
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
